      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 171,
      "message": "Yes it should. Because, mapping of relations between states-tasks-events etc happens during the model creation time itself, and there are validations for the same.\nSay for e.g., before a task reference is added to a state, first it is checked if the task is existing. Similar is the case with all related concepts.",
